description: Describes your managed prefix lists and any Amazon Web Services-managed prefix lists. To view the entries for your prefix list, use  GetManagedPrefixListEntries.

parameters.name: Filters
parameters.description: One or more filters. owner-id - The ID of the prefix list owner. prefix-list-id - The ID of the prefix list. prefix-list-name - The name of the prefix list. (dict) --- A filter name and value pair that is used to return a more specific list of results from a describe operation. Filters can be used to match a set of resources by specific criteria, such as tags, attributes, or IDs. If you specify multiple filters, the filters are joined with an AND, and the request returns only results that match all of the specified filters. For more information, see List and filter using the CLI and API in the Amazon EC2 User Guide. Name (string) --- The name of the filter. Filter names are case-sensitive. Values (list) --- The filter values. Filter values are case-sensitive. If you specify multiple values for a filter, the values are joined with an OR, and the request returns all results that match any of the specified values. (string) ---

parameters.name: PrefixListIds
parameters.description: One or more prefix list IDs. (string) ---

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token to use to retrieve the next page of results. This value is null when there are no more results to return.

nested_items.name: PrefixListId
nested_items.description: The ID of the prefix list.

nested_items.name: State
nested_items.description: The current state of the prefix list.

nested_items.name: PrefixListArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the prefix list.

nested_items.name: PrefixListName
nested_items.description: The name of the prefix list.

nested_items.name: MaxEntries
nested_items.description: The maximum number of entries for the prefix list.

nested_items.name: Version
nested_items.description: The version of the prefix list.

nested_items.name: Tags
nested_items.description: The tags for the prefix list.

nested_items.name: OwnerId
nested_items.description: The ID of the owner of the prefix list.
